OL,3,CWhat was it like to experience
OL,4,CBritain's record-breaking heatwave of
OL,5,C1976?
OL,7,FThe extraordinary heatwave of 1976 has
OL,8,Flived long in the memory of those who
OL,9,Fexperienced it. ITV News catches up
OL,10,Fwith some of them about their
OL,11,Fexperience and how it compares to the
OL,12,Fheatwaves of today.
OL,14,FThe summer of 1976 saw a British
OL,15,Fheatwave which is still recognised as
OL,16,Fone of the UK's most notable weather
OL,17,Fevents to this day.
OL,19,FIt was not a summer of one or two
OL,20,Fexceptionally hot days, but rather one
OL,21,Fof several in a row.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
