OL,3,CWhat was it like to experience
OL,4,CBritain's record-breaking heatwave of
OL,5,C1976?
OL,7,FOn 15 consecutive days between June 23
OL,8,Fand July 7, temperatures hit 32.2
OL,9,Fdegrees or higher every day.
OL,11,FThe sunshine was accompanied by a long
OL,12,Fdrought, with minimal rainfall,
OL,13,Fleading to dried-up rivers, farming
OL,14,Fdifficulties and lines of Brits
OL,15,Fqueuing in the sun to collect water.
OL,17,FBut it was also a memorable time for
OL,18,Fmany who were able to enjoy the sun.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
