OL,3,CWhat was it like to experience
OL,4,CBritain's record-breaking heatwave of
OL,5,C1976?
OL,7,F"I have very happy memories", one
OL,8,Fperson told ITV News, "I was younger
OL,9,Fthen so could cope with it!" He added.
OL,11,FAnother person said her daughter had
OL,12,Fbeen born in May of that year, "it was
OL,13,Ftrying to keep her cool and keep her
OL,14,Fhydrated when it was so very hot", she
OL,15,Frecalled.
OL,17,FOn June 28 1976, a temperature of 35.6
OL,18,Fdegrees was recorded in Hampshire,
OL,19,Fmaking it the hottest June day to date.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
