OL,3,CWhat was it like to experience
OL,4,CBritain's record-breaking heatwave of
OL,5,C1976?
OL,7,FThis record is set to be broken this
OL,8,Fweek, although it remains to be seen
OL,9,Fprecisely by how much.
OL,11,FA "heat-dome" settling over western
OL,12,FEurope could bring temperatures of up
OL,13,Fto 40C by Wednesday, with this latest
OL,14,Fheatwave expected to surpass the June
OL,15,F1976 record.
OL,17,FTemperatures could even come close to
OL,18,Fthe UK's all-time high of 40.3C
OL,19,Frecorded in July 2022 - prompting red
OL,20,Fweather warnings issued by the Met
OL,21,FOffice in areas of the UK this week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
